'''Peter N. Borsay''' is professor of history at [[Aberystwyth University]]. He is a specialist in the social, urban and [[cultural history]] of Britain.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.aber.ac.uk/en/history/staff/nnb/|title=Aberystwyth University - Borsay, Peter|publisher=|accessdate=30 April 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.history.ac.uk/history-online/teachers/teacher/borsay-peter|title=Professor Peter Borsay|publisher=|accessdate=30 April 2016}}</ref>

